snippet.title: Mushroom Patrol: The Midas Machine 2011 NCFC Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the upcoming fangame project Mushroom Patrol: The Midas Machine, made at MFGG.
This is the official NCFC 2011 trailer.
Download the demo and read more at: http://ginhost.webege.com/midasmachine

Disclaimer: This is a fangame. It is meant as a tribute to the good memories from great Nintendo games and not supposed to be sold.
